what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, multi_dimension_prefetch: Created three separate CTEs to pre-filter dimension tables (date_dim, customer_address, customer_demographics) before the main joins and EXISTS subqueries. This reduces the working set for all subsequent operations. Preserved EXISTS/NOT EXISTS semantics exactly.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out
